<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: May 3, 2026</p>

  <h2>Who we are</h2>
  <p>Howdy English is an English language learning app. We can be reached at <a href="mailto:support@howdyenglish.app">support@howdyenglish.app</a>.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Email address and password for account creation</li>
    <li>Name and native language selected during onboarding</li>
    <li>Learning activity including vocabulary saved, quizzes completed, and streaks</li>
    <li>Voice recordings submitted for pronunciation assessment</li>
    <li>Subscription status</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide and improve the app experience</li>
    <li>To track your learning progress</li>
    <li>To process subscription payments via RevenueCat</li>
    <li>To send important account-related emails</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your data. We share data only with service providers necessary to operate the app including Supabase (database), RevenueCat (payments), Deepgram (speech recognition), and Google (text to speech).</p>

  <h2>Data retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active. You may request deletion at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:support@howdyenglish.app">support@howdyenglish.app</a>.</p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>All data is encrypted in transit using HTTPS. We use Supabase for secure data storage.</p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>Howdy English is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For any privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:support@howdyenglish.app">support@howdyenglish.app</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
